                    <h1 id="td-headline" itemprop="headline">
						North Korea: The Missing Link in Northeast Asia&#8217;s Air Pollution Fight                    </h1>
					<div id="td-lead" itemprop="description"><p>South Korea and China have made progress in addressing the deadly issue of fine dust, but North Korea’s engagement is necessary too.</p>
</div>                    <div id="td-meta">
						                        <div>
							<div class="td-author">By <strong>Jihyun Cha and Taeheon Lee</strong><span style="display:none;" itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization"> for <a href="https://thediplomat.com/" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="name">The Diplomat</span></a><meta itemprop="url" content="https://thediplomat.com/2019/06/north-korea-the-missing-link-in-northeast-asias-air-pollution-fight/"><span itemprop="logo" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject"><link itemprop="url" href="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/themes/td_theme_v3/assets/logo/diplomat_logo_amp.jpg" rel="logo"><meta itemprop="width" content="600"><meta itemprop="height" content="60"></span></span></div>                            <div class="td-date"><span
