sk Intelligence</h3><i>DRI</i></header><div class="td-posts td-posts--col"><!-- flag=cache key=td:posts:section:term_45712 --><a href="/2019/11/no-pakistans-gwadar-port-is-not-a-chinese-naval-base-just-yet/" class="td-post d-1"><figure class="td-img td-post__img td-post__img--right-s"><img alt="No, Pakistan&rsquo;s Gwadar Port Is Not a Chinese Naval Base (Just Yet)" title="No, Pakistan&rsquo;s Gwadar Port Is Not a Chinese Naval Base (Just Yet)" data-sizes="(max-width: 319px) 100vw, (max-width: 752px) 138px, 219px" data-srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/thediplomat/image/upload/t_td-list-s-1/f_auto/main/2019/05/thediplomat-ap_16318589828451.jpg 138w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thediplomat/image/upload/t_td-list-s-2/f_auto/main/2019/05/thediplomat-ap_16318589828451.jpg 276w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thediplomat/image/upload/t_td-list-m-1/f_auto/main/2019/05/thediplomat-ap_16318589828451.jpg 219w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thediplomat/image/upload/t_td-list-m-2/f_auto/main/2019/05/thediplomat-ap_16318589828451.jpg 438w" data-src="https://res.cloudinary.com/thediplomat/image/upload/t_td-list-s-1/f_auto/main/2019/05/thediplomat-ap_16318589828451.jpg" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/themes/td_theme_v3/assets/img-paceholder.svg" loading="lazy"></figure><h5>November 19, 2019</h5><h4>No, Pakistan’s Gwadar Port Is Not a Chinese Naval Base (Just Yet)</h4><h6>By <span>Krzysztof Iwanek</span></h6><div>The Pakistani navy is entrenching itself in Gwadar but there is no evidence of the Chinese forces’ presence yet.</div></a><a href="/2019/11/prabowos-introductory-visit-highlights-indonesia-malaysia-defense-relations/" class="td-post d-2"><figure class="td-img td-post__img td-post__img--right-s"><img alt="Prabowo&amp;#8217;s Introductory Visit Highlights Indonesia-Malaysia Defense Relations" title="Prabowo&amp;#8217;s Introductory Visit Highlights Indonesia-Malaysia Defense Relations" data-sizes="(max-width: 319px) 100vw, (max-width: 752px) 138px, 219px" data-srcset="htt